This Job simply launch the iperf command.

Required Arguments:
  type : you have to specify if you want to launch a server or a client

Optionnal Arguments:
  all the arguments taken by the iperf command

Statistics: it doesn't produce any statistic

Example:
  - Launch an iperf server : -a "mode -s"
  - Lannch an iperf client that will connect with the server in 172.20.0.83 : -a "mode -c 172.20.0.83" 

